Selects the allocation size used to assign mmioh resources. Total mmioh space can be up to 32xgranularity. Per stack mmioh resource assignments are multiples of the granularity where 1 unit per stack is the default allocation. Note:When MMIOH granularity size is 1024G, the MMIOH base can not be selected as 56T or 3.5T, In addition, the combination of 40T and 1024G is not available with 8 processors.
